th adults and children to unwind and have fun. Gino Paradise also boasts top-quality fitness and dining facilities, ensuring you can spend a whole day enjoying the various offerings.  Reaching the Tbilisi Sea is straightforward, whether you're using a taxi app from the city center or taking a mini-bus (Marshutka) #432 from Sarajishvili Metro station. The journey offers a unique opportunity to enjoy Tbilisi's urban landscapes before arriving at this serene retreat.  In summary, the Tbilisi Sea offers a rich blend of history, art, recreation, and natural beauty. Whether you're an adventure-seeker, a history enthusiast, an art lover, or just someone seeking relaxation, this destination offers something for everyone.",
